BC1AUD.original: ~z~you and I don't know each other.
~z~You don't understand the way I suffer. I need to go in that park.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~你不明白咱受的什么苦，咱必须去公园。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I can't go on. Do it alone Niko.
~z~You picked the wrong queen, didn't you?
~z~I wish we could all just get along.
~z~Niko, you're still in great shape. You work out?
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，你身材保持得很不错啊，平常健身吗？

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I thought we didn't know each other.
~z~He'll only come after me if it looks like I'm by myself.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~他只会趁咱孤身一人的时候袭击咱。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I knew you were the right person to call.
~z~I'm going to kick the shit out of you.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~我会把你打到亲妈都不认识。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Sorry, love. You were born in the wrong century.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~抱歉了，亲爱的，你生不逢时啊。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~If he leaves me, I'll kill myself.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~要是他甩了咱，咱就要自杀了。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Let's get our heart rates up, Niko. Remember to hang back, I need to charm him out.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~先热身暖暖身子，Niko。记得离远点，咱得把他引出来。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Whatever you say, buddy. Unfortunately, for hitting my friend,
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~你爱咋说咋说，小子。只可惜，你打的是我朋友。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Now I'm a monster - an old, wrinkly, gray monster.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~现在咱只是个怪物——又老又皱的老怪物。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I have to jog. How am I going to keep fit? One ounce of cellulite and Bryce will leave me.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱必须跑步，不然怎么保持身材？多一块赘肉Bryce都会立马甩掉咱的。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Is there a name for that fitness plan? I'd take a class if I could be guaranteed buns like yours.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~你的健身计划有名字吗？要是能有你这么结实的屁股，咱也想学一学。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I'm sorry, I just see him running and I need to grab him and just...
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~对不起，我看着他跑步就想抓住他...

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Catch him Niko. This man has haunted my dreams for weeks.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~追上他，Niko。这人害咱连做了好几个星期恶梦。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Flor... Bernie. Don't go jogging for a while. He's still out there.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~Flor...Bernie。暂时先别去跑步了，他还在外面。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Not really. I keep active, you know.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~并不是，只是活动比较多，你懂的。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I'm coming with you honey. Make some room.
~z~How can you say that? I thought you were different!
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~你怎么能这么说？咱还以为你跟那些俗人不同！

BC1AUD.original: ~z~We're going for a jog, Niko. Try to keep up. And stay back too, we don't want to be rumbled.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱们要准备跑步了，Niko。尽量跟上，但别跟太近，咱可不想被看出来。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~It's the TV man. They just rub it in your face all day long. All those... men.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~是电视里的人，他们老是对着你的脸戳你的痛处。全部的...人。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Scooch up Niko. Bernie is riding shotgun.
~z~Niko, I want you at my rear.
~z~Mr. Macho is making me gray and flabby.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~直男先生让咱变得又老又胖。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I've gotten fat and ugly, Niko. You should have seen me when I first got here.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱现在是又胖又丑，Niko。你应该看看咱刚来这里时有多好看。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~He's not going to come out if you're that close.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~你跟这么近他怎么会出来呢。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Niko, he got me. Where were you? I thought you were watching me?
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，他打到我了。你在哪？你没有替我盯着吗？

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I only wanted to mess with one of you!
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~我只是想捉弄你们中的一个！

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I can't believe that Bryce hasn't ended things already. I'm disgusting.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~真不敢相信Bryce还没把事情摆平，咱吐了。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Every time I go out jogging, and doing aerobics or playing ultimate disc,
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~每次咱去跑步，做有氧运动或者玩极限飞盘的时候，

BC1AUD.original: ~z~It's cardio time, Niko. Remember to keep some distance though.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~现在是健身时间，Niko。记得和我保持点距离。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I can't stand it. I gotta go.
~z~I just feel sorry for you, sweetie.
~z~I was going too fast... too fast.
~z~I can't get beaten up by boyfriends.
~z~He's not going to attack you again.
~z~Oh shit. This wasn't meant to happen.
~z~It was hardly the most progressive place. How does my hair look?
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~这算哪门子的开明社会啊。咱的头发怎么样？

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I won't stand it... it's not fair. I'm just being me!
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱也忍不了...太不公平了。咱只是做咱自己！

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I'm going home for a shower and an avocado face pack.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱要回家洗个澡敷面膜去了。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~You are good enough to eat. Fun time soon. Fun time. I promise.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~你可以放心吃东西了，马上好戏上场了，好戏，我保证。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~It's me. I'm the problem. My daddy never loved me.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~是我，我的错，我爸爸从来没爱过我。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I think I know how to make this guy accept you.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~我大概知道怎么让这家伙接受你。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~You messed with the wrong queen, loser.
~z~It's my hiney that I'm worried about honey, get be-hiney me.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱担心的是咱的后庭，亲爱的，到我后头去。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~The haters are trying to kill me... I can't stand it.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~有仇同者想杀咱...咱受不了了。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I'm a prisoner in my own home.
~z~There's no way the hater's going to think I'm alone with you clamped to my buns like that.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~仇同者看你贴咱屁股这么近，不可能会觉得咱是一个人跑步的。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I wish people would just accept me for who I am, you know, the good and the bad?
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱只希望别人能接受咱的为人，你懂吗？优点和缺点都是。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~We can't let him lose us, sweetie.
~z~Niko, I need you to watch my behind.
~z~I keep thinking I'm being followed, and I don't know why.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱一直都觉得有人跟踪我，也不知道为什么。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~to get away from small minded, angry macho pricks...
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~远离那些心胸狭隘的暴躁直男癌...
~z~抱歉，亲爱的。你让咱俩暴露了。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Dancing in Hercules with my shirt off - every eye in the room was on me.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~在大力神里裸衣热舞——咱就是全场的焦点。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Go hold hands or something, leave me alone.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~你们自己去牵手吧，别来找我。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Get him, Niko. I want him to suffer for every gray hair and worry line.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~追上他，Niko，咱要让他为每根白发和皱纹付出代价。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I do my exercises in Middle Park, Niko.
~z~Ooo! I am so glad you've come back into my life.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~嚯！你能回到咱的生活中咱真高兴。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I don't feel comfortable if you're not behind me.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~你不在咱身后咱会很不安的。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~He's got away. We ain't gonna catch him.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~他跑掉了。我们现在抓不了他了。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Shit man, I didn't mean nothing by it.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~靠，伙计，我不是有意那么做的。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~You'll have no more trouble Bernie. Don't worry.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~你不会再遇到问题了，Bernie。别担心。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Okay, Bernie, let's go out and have a look.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~好了，Bernie，那我们就出去看一看吧。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~The haters are in Middle Park, hon.
~z~no one's going to pay attention to me.
~z~You thought this was going to be easy, didn't you?
~z~Come on big boy. Use all you got on him.
~z~Stay back Niko. Play hard to get.
~z~Sometimes I think it's a godsend that Bryce has to go back to his wife for the night instead of sleeping with me.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~有时咱都觉得Bryce晚上回去不跟咱睡跟老婆睡已经是万幸了。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I came to this country to be myself...
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱来这个国家就是为了活出真我...

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I'm going to rot in my apartment. The mummy of Middle Park West they'll call me.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱要烂在自己的家里了。他们会管我叫西中心公园木乃伊的。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Bernie, what's the deal? Are you asleep or something? Wake up.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~Bernie，什么情况？你睡着了还是咋了？快醒醒。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~It's called getting chased by the cops and being errand boy for the mob.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~这计划叫「被警察追捕，做黑帮马仔」。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Bryce only likes carpet burns he's given me. Not these things.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~Bryce喜欢拿他的络腮胡扎我，可不是这些东西。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Watch your skinny frappes, Bernie's coming through.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~注意你们的刨冰饮料什么的，Bernie要过来了。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~The man we chase is a monster, not you.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~我们追的那人才是怪物，你不是。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Because we want this guy to attack you. Come on.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~因为这样那家伙才会袭击你。来吧。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I don't take it lying down, hater.
~z~I'm here, I'm queer, deal with it.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱就在这，咱就是同性恋，来搞我啊。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~No siree, you think I look like this when I get up in the morning?
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~不，先生，你以为咱早上起来就现在这样吗？

BC1AUD.original: ~z~~c~Speak English.~s~ And I told you, it's Bernie.
~z~You must have been abused as a child.
~z~It takes hours of plucking and buffing before I can even bear to look at myself.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱得花好几小时化妆、抛光，不然咱自己都不敢看咱的脸。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Hold back the tears, Florian. Wait until we get this guy.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~别急着哭，Florian。等我们抓住他再哭。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Niko, this isn't working sweetie. Either the hater has seen us and he'll stay away.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，这样不管用啊，甜心。要么他发现咱俩然后走掉。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~No he ain't. You're an absolute sweetie Niko Bellic. I never would have thought it.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~是不会了。你对咱真是太好了，Niko Bellic。没想到你人这么好。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I better not need plastic surgery on these cuts.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~我可不想为这些伤口做手术。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I need an ice pack Niko, but get that guy first!
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱需要个冰袋，Niko。不过先抓住那家伙！

BC1AUD.original: ~z~This soldier's out of action. Finish the mission without him.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~属下失去作战能力。抛下他完成任务。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~That was Florian... urgh. Bernie was beautiful when he arrived on the scene.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~那个是Florian...呃。Bernie刚来那会儿真是英俊潇洒啊。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~I'll tell you, I don't look fabulous when I'm waking up with cold sweats at all hours of the night.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~咱跟你说，咱在晚上冒着冷汗惊醒的样子可不好看。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Or someone's going to tell Bryce I'm with you and he'll think I'm cheating.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~要么会有人告诉Bryce咱跟你在一起，然后他会觉得咱出了轨。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~There are so many young, fit men out there. He could have anyone.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~外面年轻健美的男人有的是，他变心了都说不准。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Get ready Niko. You and I are about to get real close.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~准备好，Niko。你和咱会亲密接触的。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~We need to get out of here
~z~Niko Bellic that is the sweetest thing you have ever said to me. I think I'm going to cry.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~Niko Bellic，这是你对咱说过的最甜的话了。咱都要感动哭了。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~Why don't you pick on someone who'll fight back?
~z~I knew you before you got here.
~z~They don't call it beauty sleep for nothing.
BC1AUD.translated: ~z~美容觉这个说法可不是编出来玩的。

BC1AUD.original: ~z~some guy comes up and threatens me.
